<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <style>
    .email-container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      color: #333;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .earnings-info {
      background-color: #e9f7ef;
      border: 1px solid #d5f5e3;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .amount {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #16a085;
      display: block;
      text-align: center;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .button {
      background-color: #007bff;
      color: white;
      padding: 12px 25px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      display: inline-block;
      margin: 10px 0;
    }
    .button-green {
      background-color: #28a745;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #666;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="email-container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Earnings Now Available</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <p>Hello {{hostName}},</p>
      <p>Good news! Your earnings are now available for payout.</p>

      <span class="amount">{{totalAmount}}</span>

      <div class="earnings-info">
        <p>You have earnings available from {{bookingsCount}} completed bookings. You can now request a payout to your bank account.</p>
      </div>

      <center>
        <a href="{{payoutUrl}}" class="button button-green">Request Payout</a>
        <br>
        <a href="{{earningsUrl}}" class="button">View Earnings</a>
      </center>

      <p>Thank you for hosting with us!</p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>Need help? Contact our support team at {{supportEmail}}</p>
      <p>Â© {{year}} {{companyName}}. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>